{"sn35.107:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 35.107 ","sn35.107:0.2":"11. Yogakkhemivagga ","sn35.107:0.3":"Lokasamudayasutta ","sn35.107:1.1":"“Lokassa, bhikkhave, samudayanca atthangamanca desessami. ","sn35.107:1.2":"Tam sunatha. ","sn35.107:1.3":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, lokassa samudayo? ","sn35.107:1.4":"Cakkhunca paticca rupe ca uppajjati cakkhuvinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn35.107:1.5":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn35.107:1.6":"vedanapaccaya tanha; ","sn35.107:1.7":"tanhapaccaya upadanam; ","sn35.107:1.8":"upadanapaccaya bhavo; ","sn35.107:1.9":"bhavapaccaya jati; ","sn35.107:1.10":"jatipaccaya jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa sambhavanti. ","sn35.107:1.11":"Ayam kho, bhikkhave, lokassa samudayo …pe… ","sn35.107:1.12":"jivhanca paticca rase ca uppajjati jivhavinnanam …pe… ","sn35.107:1.13":"mananca paticca dhamme ca uppajjati manovinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn35.107:1.14":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn35.107:1.15":"vedanapaccaya tanha; ","sn35.107:1.16":"tanhapaccaya upadanam; ","sn35.107:1.17":"upadanapaccaya bhavo; ","sn35.107:1.18":"bhavapaccaya jati; ","sn35.107:1.19":"jatipaccaya jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa sambhavanti. ","sn35.107:1.20":"Ayam kho, bhikkhave, lokassa samudayo. ","sn35.107:2.1":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, lokassa atthangamo? ","sn35.107:2.2":"Cakkhunca paticca rupe ca uppajjati cakkhuvinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn35.107:2.3":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn35.107:2.4":"vedanapaccaya tanha. ","sn35.107:2.5":"Tassayeva tanhaya asesaviraganirodha upadananirodho; ","sn35.107:2.6":"upadananirodha bhavanirodho; ","sn35.107:2.7":"bhavanirodha jatinirodho; ","sn35.107:2.8":"jatinirodha jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa nirujjhanti. ","sn35.107:2.9":"Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti. ","sn35.107:2.10":"Ayam kho, bhikkhave, lokassa atthangamo …pe… ","sn35.107:2.11":"jivhanca paticca rase ca uppajjati …pe… ","sn35.107:2.12":"mananca paticca dhamme ca uppajjati manovinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn35.107:2.13":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn35.107:2.14":"vedanapaccaya tanha. ","sn35.107:2.15":"Tassayeva tanhaya asesaviraganirodha upadananirodho; ","sn35.107:2.16":"upadananirodha …pe… ","sn35.107:2.17":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti. ","sn35.107:2.18":"Ayam kho, bhikkhave, lokassa atthangamo”ti. ","sn35.107:2.19":"Catuttham. "}